%20Amit%20Shah%20ji%E2%80%99s%20washing%20machine%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20middle%20seat%20on%20an%20airplane%20is%20severely%20underrated%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22996%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22middle%20seat%20skitch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5880fa5955b1061d008b5638%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20middle%20seat%20has%20long%20been%20maligned%20as%20the%20worst%20seat%20on%20a%20plane.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20recent%20trip%20helped%20me%20realize%20there%20are%20actually%20benefits%20to%20the%20middle%20seat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAisle%20and%20window%20seats%20aren't%20all%20they%20are%20cracked%20up%20to%20be%2C%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWindow%20or%20aisle%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20seats%20might%20only%20be%20a%20few%20feet%20apart%2C%20but%20an%20ideological%20chasm%20exists%20between%20them.%20You%20fall%20into%20one%20of%20the%20two%20camps%2C%20and%20allegiances%20don't%20switch%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeat%20selection%20is%20all%20the%20more%20important%20these%20days%20after%20an%20Alaska%20Airlines%20flight%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-airlines-flight-window-portland-oregon-california-2024-1%5C%22%3Elost%20part%20of%20its%20fuselage%20mid-flight%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(No%20serious%20injuries%20were%20reported%2C%20thanks%20largely%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-airlines-plane-door-plug-two-most-damaged-seats-empty-2024-1%5C%22%3Etwo%20seats%20directly%20next%20to%20the%20blown-out%20window%20being%20empty%3C%2Fa%3E.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20as%20we%20reexamine%20our%20preferred%20seats%2C%20what%20about%20what's%20between%20the%20window%20and%20aisle%3F%20Like%20yellow%20Starbursts%2C%20we%20all%20deal%20with%20the%20middle%20seat%2C%20but%20most%20of%20us%20don't%20prefer%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20be%20sandwiched%20between%20two%20strangers%20when%20you%20can%20have%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20aisle%20or%20the%20comfort%20of%20a%20window%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20staunch%20member%20of%20Team%20Aisle%2C%20I%20was%20distraught%20to%20get%20stuck%20with%20a%20middle%20seat%20on%20a%20recent%20flight%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Las%20Vegas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20bigger%20guy%20%E2%80%94%206'2%26quot%3B%20and%20nearly%20220%20pounds%20depending%20on%20my%20takeout%20order%20%E2%80%94%20flying%20middle%20for%20a%20five-plus%20hour%20trip%20didn't%20sound%20like%20a%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I'm%20here%20to%20tell%20you%20I%20was%20wrong.%20I%20now%20kneel%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20the%20middle%20seat%2C%20and%20you%20should%2C%20too.%20Here's%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEveryone%20feels%20sorry%20for%20the%20middle%20seat%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20and%20biggest%20benefit%20of%20sitting%20middle%20isn't%20immediately%20obvious%20until%20you've%20spent%20time%20in%20the%20seat.%20But%20once%20there%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%3A%20Your%20seatmates%20feel%20bad%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20recent%20trip%20to%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20my%20aisle%20partner%20quickly%20told%20me%20I%20was%20welcome%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eentire%3C%2Fem%3E%20armrest%20we%20shared.%20My%20window%20buddy%20didn't%20make%20the%20same%20offer%2C%20but%20he%20seemed%20to%20be%20leaning%20so%20far%20away%20from%20me%20that%20you%20would%20have%20thought%20I%20was%20radioactive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stigma%20around%20middle%20seats%20has%20meant%20aisle%20and%20window%20passengers%20tend%20to%20give%20those%20stuck%20there%20more%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20the%20aisle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20you're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faisle-seats-are-better-than-window-seats-on-flights-2024-1%5C%22%3Eall%20in%20on%20the%20aisle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20so%2C%20I%20have%20some%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20like%20getting%20up%205%20times%20a%20flight%20so%20your%20seatmates%20can%20use%20the%20restroom%3F%20Do%20you%20enjoy%20your%20shoulders%20and%20elbows%20getting%20crushed%20by%20passengers%20and%20flight%20attendants%20constantly%20walking%20down%20the%20aisle%3F%20Is%20it%20fun%20having%20random%20crotches%20or%20butts%20in%20your%20direct%20eye%20line%20as%20people%20randomly%20decide%20to%20stand%20in%20the%20aisle%20for%2030%20minutes%20mid-flight%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20get%20better%20when%20the%20plane%20lands.%20Nothing%20like%20having%20people%20aggressively%20push%20up%20the%20aisle%20before%20the%20door%20is%20even%20open.%20We're%20in%20row%2027%2C%20sir.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20while.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESitting%20in%20the%20window%20is%20a%20lesson%20in%20negotiation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20set%20aside%20recently%20unlocked%20fears%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-airlines-flight-could-have-been-much-more-tragic-ntsb-2024-1%5C%22%3Esitting%20next%20to%20a%20window%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20thought%20around%20window%20seats%20has%20long%20been%20that%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20in%20the%20plane.%20You%20can%20exist%20unbothered%20by%20the%20comings%20and%20goings%20of%20your%20fellow%20passengers.%20You%20have%20a%20nice%20wall%20to%20rest%20your%20head%20on%20if%20you%20want%20to%20sleep.%20And%20you%20can%20take%20pictures%20of%20the%20clouds%20to%20notify%20your%20500%20Instagram%20followers%20you%20are%20traveling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unless%20you%20have%20a%20steel%20bladder%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20use%20the%20restroom%20during%20a%20long%20flight.%20That%20means%20negotiating%20across%20two%20passengers%20for%20an%20escape.%20God%20forbid%20it's%20a%20red-eye%2C%20and%20they're%20sleeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20bathroom%20trips%20that%20become%20a%20headache.%20Since%20windows%20don't%20always%20line%20up%20evenly%20with%20seats%2C%20sometimes%20that%20means%20sharing%20it%20with%20the%20row%20in%20front%20or%20behind%20you.%20Does%20it%20stay%20up%3F%20Can%20we%20put%20it%20down%3F%20What%20about%20halfway%3F%20Your%20trip%20to%20LAX%20is%20now%20a%20crash%20course%20in%20diplomacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMiddle%20seats%20are%20cheaper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20you're%20still%20not%20sold%20on%20the%20middle.%20If%20the%20above%20arguments%20aren't%20speaking%20to%20you%2C%20maybe%20a%20financial%20one%20will.%20Middle%20seats%20are%20almost%20always%20cheaper%20than%20aisles%20or%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20airlines%20are%20the%20kings%20of%20nickel%20and%20diming%20their%20customers%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bluxury%26quot%3B%20or%20being%20able%20to%20pick%20a%20window%20or%20aisle%20seat%20almost%20always%20requires%20an%20upgraded%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20they're%20just%20giving%20out%20middle%20seats%20at%20no%20extra%20charge.%20What%20a%20time%20to%20be%20alive!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPS-%20This%20philosophy%20only%20extends%20to%20three-seaters.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20middle%20seat%20in%20a%20four-seater%2C%20may%20God%20have%20mercy%20on%20your%20soul.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairplane-middle-seat-not-bad-aisle-window-travel-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705843561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6536a1c696f7540cd0631a09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairplane-middle-seat-not-bad-aisle-window-travel-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2