20prices%20will%20be%20fueled%20by%20several%20factors%2C%20Ziminsky%20and%20Kinney%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20the%20supply%20of%20available%20diamonds%20will%20become%20even%20tighter%20this%20year.%20That's%20a%20reversal%20from%202023%2C%20when%20diamond%20producers%2C%20who%20shuttered%20mining%20activity%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20ended%20up%20overproducing%20diamonds%2C%20causing%20prices%20to%20tumble.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEfforts%20are%20already%20underway%20to%20tighten%20supply%2C%20Ziminsky%20said%2C%20with%20some%20suppliers%20halting%20mining%20activity%20altogether.%20The%20Russian%20mining%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fdiamond-market-crash-russia-ban-prices-sanctions-alrosa-de-beer-2023-9%5C%22%3EAlrosa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20paused%20sales%20of%20rough%20diamonds%20for%20two%20months%20last%20year%20to%20boost%20prices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETighter%20supply%20will%20be%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20G7's%20recent%20ban%20on%20Russian%20diamonds%2C%20Kinney%20added%2C%20as%20Russia%20is%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20pass%20off%20its%20diamonds%20off%20to%20Chinese%20and%20Indian%20refiners%2C%20who%20can%20then%20sell%20them%20to%20the%20West.%20That%20could%20slash%20another%2030%25%20of%20the%20world's%20diamond%20supply%20off%20the%20market%2C%20he%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20begin%20to%20see%20inventory%20levels%20normalize.%20And%20once%20that%20happens%2C%20we'll%20start%20to%20see%20natural%20diamond%20prices%20recover%2C%26quot%3B%20Ziminsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20is%20also%20about%20to%20heat%20up%20after%20an%20anemic%202023.%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20whom%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-luxury-jewelry-resale-market-is-booming-during-the-pandemic-2020-9%5C%22%3Esplurged%20on%20goods%20like%20expensive%20jewlery%20during%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20had