come%20from%20unexpected%20places%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Saturday%20evening%20Mass%2C%20I%20smiled%20at%20an%20older%20man%20who%20ushered%20every%20week.%20He'd%20always%20smiled%20at%20me%20as%20he%20walked%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20church%20to%20grab%20the%20baskets%20for%20the%20weekly%20collection.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20he%20walked%20to%20my%20pew%20and%20whispered%20that%20one%20of%20the%20usual%20ushers%20wasn't%20available%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20help%20take%20up%20the%20collection%20with%20him%20and%20another%20older%20man%20who%20usually%20helped%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20ushers%20are%20usually%20men.%20Women%20are%20also%20welcome%20to%20usher%2C%20but%20traditionally%2C%20most%20churches%20tend%20to%20attract%20men%20in%20their%2070s%20and%2080s%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-dog-at-shelter-volunteer-at-is-teaching-me-resiliency-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evolunteer%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20immediately%20agreed%20to%20help%20him%2C%20surprised%20he%20approached%20me%20to%20ask%20for%20help%20rather%20than%20the%20older%20men%20sitting%20near%20me.%20Later%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20the%20usher%2C%20whose%20name%20was%20Art%2C%20thought%20I%20had%20a%20warm%20smile%20and%20seemed%20friendly.%20I%20thought%20the%20same%20thing%20about%20him!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20happy%20to%20learn%20that%20despite%20growing%20up%20in%20The%20Silent%20Generation%2C%20when%20Masses%20had%20very%20distinct%20traditions%20and%20rules%2C%20those%20born%20at%20that%20time%20may%20be%20more%20forward-thinking%20than%20I%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kate%20and%20Art%2C%20both%20smiling%20and%20wearing%20yellow%20shirts.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aaacfb43bb77284b9e89f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKate%20and%20Art%20met%20while%20ushering%20at%20church.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EYou%20never%20quite%20feel%20as%20old%20as%20you%20are%2C%20whether%20you're%2035%20or%2085%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F101-year-old-neurologist-shares-four-keys-long-happy-life-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung-at-heart%3C%2Fa%3E%20clich%C3%A9%20is%20actually%20quite%20true.%20Ever%20since%20that%20evening%20I%20helped%20usher%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20becoming%20a%20regular%20at%205%20p.m.%20Saturday%20Masses.%20I%20became%20close%20to%20Art%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20other%20man%20who%20helped%20that%20night%2C%20who%20was%20named%20Jack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%2C%20who%20was%20also%20in%20his%2080s%2C%20was%20the%20head%20of%20a%20thriving%20auto%20empire.%20I%20admired%20how%20humble%20he%20was.%20He%20had%20money%2C%20but%20you'd%20never%20know%20it.%20Along%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-found-love-in-our-seventies-got-married-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecouple%20I%20met%20who%20was%20in%20their%2070s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Art%20and%20Jack%20would%20watch%20out%20for%20me%20and%20always%20make%20sure%20I%20got%20home%20safely%2C%20offering%20rides%20to%20and%20from%20church.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I'm%20in%20my%2030s%2C%20I%20often%20still%20feel%20like%20a%20teenager%20when%20I%20put%20on%20the%20music%20I%20listened%20to%20decades%20ago%2C%20like%20the%20Spice%20Girls%20and%20Britney%20Spears.%20It%20was%20refreshing%20to%20me%20to%20learn%20that%20Art%20also%20stayed%20connected%20to%20his%20interests%20from%20childhood.%20He%20had%20an%20elaborate%20model%20train%20village%20in%20the%20crawl%20space%20in%20his%20basement%20that%20he%20had%20been%20adding%20to%20for%20decades.%20He%20wore%20a%20train%20conductor%20hat%20when%20he%20showed%20off%20the%20space%2C%20getting%20the%20same%20twinkle%20in%20his%20eye%20that%20he%20probably%20h