0(%40softiealiaa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsoftiealiaa%2Fstatus%2F1748893537176031402%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20work%20front%2C%20Alia%20Bhatt%20was%20nominated%20for%20Best%20Actor%20In%20A%20Leading%20Role%20(Female)%20award%20for%20her%20performance%20in%20Karan%20Johar's%20Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%20at%20the%20Filmfare%20Awards%202024.%20The%2069th%20edition%20of%20the%20award%20ceremony%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Gujarat%20on%20January%2027%20and%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705837440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fqhp6tqkg_alia-_625x300_21_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fjust-alia-bhatt-slaying-as-usual-in-a-saree-at-joy-awards-2024-4904687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharing%20pictures%20from%20the%20event%2C%20Alia%20Bhatt%20simply%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20a%20night%20of%20culture%2C%20honour%20%26amp%3B%20cinema%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fjust-alia-bhatt-slaying-as-usual-in-a-saree-at-joy-awards-2024-4904687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fjust-alia-bhatt-slaying-as-usual-in-a-saree-at-joy-awards-2024-4904687%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fjust-alia-bhatt-slaying-as-usual-in-a-saree-at-joy-awards-2024-4904687%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOuter%20Wall%2C%206%20Temples%2C%202%20Idols%26quot%3B%3A%20Sneak%20Peek%20Into%20Ram%20Mandir%20Complex%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFive%20structures%20and%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20are%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20complex%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20where%20the%20'Pran%20Pratistha'%20ceremony%20will%20be%20held%20to%20mark%20its%20grand%20opening%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Shri%20Ram%20Mandir%20Construction%20Committee%20chairperson%20Nripendra%20Mishra%20narrates%20how%20the%20devotees%20will%20find%20their%20way%20to%20the%20main%20idol%20in%20the%20temple%20area%20spread%20over%202.7%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotees%20will%20first%20cross%20an%20outer%20wall%20that%20surrounds%20the%20main%20structures.%20The%20795-metre%20'parkota'%20will%20have%20five%20temples%20and%20garv%20gruha%20(sanctum%20sanctorum)%20inside%2C%20which%20will%20have%20the%20main%20idol%20and%20allow%20devotees%20to%20do%20parikrama%2C%20said%20Mr%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20in%20front%20of%20the%20garv%20gruha%2C%20there%20are%20five%20mandaps%20in%20the%20temple%20and%20the%20total%20length%20of%20the%20temple%20from%20the%20garv%20gruha%20to%20the%20first%20stair%20point%20is%20roughly%20about%20400%20feet%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20Ram%20temple%20panel%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20had%20earlier%20claimed%20the%20temple%20was%20designed%20to%20last%20over%20a%20thousand%20years.%20No%20iron%20or%20steel%20has%20been%20used%20for%20its%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20electronic%20sensors%20have%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20temple's%20foundation%20to%20find%20out%20if%20there's%20any%20impact%20on%20its%20stones%20due%20to%20earthquake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20sensors%20will%20convey%20if%20any%20movement%20in%20stones%20or%20external%20factors%20like%20an%20earthquake%20has%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20temple.%20This%20is%20being%20studied%20regularly%20by%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20(construction%20firm).%20They%20will%20continue%20for%20a%20few%20years%20on%20a%20contract%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sensory%20reports%20are%20forwarded%20to%20the%20Central%20Building%20Research%20Institute%20in%20Roorkee%2C%20which%20carries%20out%20research%20on%20construction%20solutions%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20or%20the%20child%20Ram%2C%20will%20be%20in%20the%20garv%20gruha%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20temple%20complex.%20This%20portion%20of%20the%20temple%20is%20completed%2C%20said%20Mr%20Mishra%2C%20clarifying%20the%20doubts%20on%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20temple's%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20portion%20where%20construction%20is%20still%20going%20on%20is%20the%20first%20floor%20that%20will%20house%20the%20Ram%20Darbar.%20Here%2C%20the%20idol%20of%20King%20Ram%20will%20be%20accompanied%20by%20Sita%2C%20his%20brothers%2C%20and%20Hanuman%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20floor%20will%20host%20religious%20observances%20approved%20by%20the%20temple%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20two%20Ram%20Lalla%20idols%20in%20the%20garv%20gruha%20-%20the%20main%20black%20stone%20idol%20and%20the%20one%20that%20is%20being%20worshipped%20in%20the%20temporary%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idol%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bbelieved%20to%20have%20appeared%20in%201947%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20moved%20to%20the%20new%20temple%20this%20evening%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecorations%20are%20in%20full%20swing%20at%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20for%20tomorrow's%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20ceremony%20that%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20a%20host%20of%20prominent%20personalities%20from%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20500%20volunteers%20are%20working%20day%20and%20night%20to%20help%20the%20temple%20trust's%20general%20secretary%20Champat%20Rai%20in%20organizing%20the%20event%2C%20said%20Mr%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705837320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F2q9dcv9g_ayodhya-ram-temple-pti_625x300_21_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-outer-wall-6-temples-2-idols-sneak-peek-into-