20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2Flocal%2Fphoenix%2F2023%2F12%2F19%2Freal-estate-metro-phoenix-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efewest%20sales%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20around%20the%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETy%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20central%20Ohio%2C%20where%20he%20found%20work%20at%20a%20large%20insurance%20company.%20As%20he%20built%20his%20way%20up%2C%20he%20accepted%20a%20promotion%20that%20allowed%20him%20to%20move%20to%20Florida%20with%20his%20family%2C%20where%20he%20lived%20in%20the%20early%202000s.%20He%20enjoyed%20Florida%2C%20though%20he%20accepted%20another%20promotion%20in%20Kentucky%2C%20then%20West%20Virginia%2C%20ultimately%20followed%20by%20one%20in%20the%20Indianapolis%20area%20%E2%80%94%20all%20with%20the%20same%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20younger%20in%20my%20career%2C%20I%20took%20the%20positions%20I%20needed%20to%20take%20to%20be%20somewhere%20I%20want%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Ty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Overland%20Park%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftopeka-kansas-jobs-cost-of-living-real-estate-investment-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EKansas%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20another%20work%20opportunity.%20He%20said%20the%20city%20was%20a%20great%20place%20to%20raise%20a%20family%20and%20was%20quite%20diverse.%20The%20area%20was%20a%20hub%20for%20healthcare%2C%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20was%20lower%20than%20some%20other%20cities%20he%20lived%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20nears%20retirement%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20presented%20with%20a%20few%20options%20for%20where%20to%20move%20next%20both%20for%20work%20opportunities%20and%20retirement%20long-term.%20He%20decided%20between%20Phoenix%2C%20Nashville%2C%20and%20Tampa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhoenix%20suited%20his%20professional%20and%20retirement%20goals%20the%20best.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-regrets-i-moved-from-boston-to-kansas-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EKansas%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20an%20income%20tax%20of%205.7%25%20on%20income%20above%20%2430%2C000%2C%20Arizona%20has%20an%20income%20tax%20of%202.5%25.%20While%20Florida%20has%20no%20income%20tax%2C%20he%20was%20drawn%20in%20more%20by%20the%20Phoenix%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20housing%20would%20be%20more%20expensive%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20though.%20His%20home%20in%20Phoenix%20is%20about%20half%20the%20size%20and%20slightly%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20%24260%2C000%20price%20tag%20of%20his%20Kansas%20home.%20Though%20he%20expects%20there's%20still%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20home%20value%20appreciation%2C%20and%20he%20said%20his%20home%20still%20comes%20in%20well%20below%20comparable%20prices%20in%20major%20California%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20it%20would%20somewhat%20balance%20out%20over%20the%20years%20though%2C%20as%20most%20of%20his%20daily%20expenses%20from%20food%20to%20auto%20and%20home%20insurance%20are%20cheaper%20in%20Phoenix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20getting%20the%20overall%20reduction%20in%20the%20tax%20burden%2C%20the%20overall%20cost%20of%20living%20outside%20of%20housing%20was%20cheaper%2C%20my%20utilities%20are%20cheaper%2C%26quot%3B%20Ty%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20looked%20at%20the%20overall%20expenditures%20that%20I%20would%20have%2C%20it%20was%2020%25%20to%2025%25%20more%2C%20but%20in%20return%2C%20I%20was%20getting%20good%20year-round%20weather%2C%20ease%20of%20travel%2C%20looking%20into%20the%20lower%20future%20tax%20burden%20when%20I%20start%20to%20get%20into%20my%20401(k).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20seen%20prices%20for%20homes%20fall%20over%20the%20last%20year%20in%20Phoenix%20and%20nearby%20Scottsdale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20some%20recent%20stuff%20we're%20hearing%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20mortgage%20rates%20going%20down