-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20influx%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20tech%20workers%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20city%20has%20also%20become%20an%20insurance%20and%20financial%20services%20hub%20that's%20attracting%20younger%20professionals%20from%20other%20major%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETy%20said%20that%20Phoenix%20is%20where%20he%20sees%20himself%20staying%20for%20the%20future%2C%20as%20he's%20not%20ready%20to%20retire%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20at%20a%20stage%20in%20my%20life%20where%20I'm%20not%20looking%20for%20that%20next%20career%2C%20but%20I'm%20also%20looking%20at%20what%20can%20I%20do%20to%20ensure%20I'm%20set%20up%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20my%20life%2C%20and%20then%20I%20have%20something%20that%20I%20can%20pass%20on%20to%20generations%20in%20the%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Ty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20moved%20to%20a%20new%20state%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-phoenix-weather-kansas-overland-park-cost-of-living-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705837081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d3e763cc84b4dfaffb123%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-phoenix-weather-kansas-overland-park-cost-of-living-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Gen%20Xer%20moved%20last%20year%20from%20Overland%20Park%2C%20Kansas%2C%20to%20Phoenix%20for%20work.%20His%20Phoenix%20home%20costs%20more%20for%20less%20space%2C%20but%20his%20other%20daily%20expenses%20are%20less.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40insider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22can