0something%20in%20the%20wider%20world%20go%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHomesteaders%20reject%20the%20status%20quo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20homesteaders%20live%20on%20remote%20farms%20or%20ranches%20and%20raise%20livestock.%20Others%20live%20in%20more%20urban%20areas%20and%20maintain%20small%20container%20gardens.%20Many%20homeschool%20their%20children.%20They%20often%20opt%20for%20solar%20panels%20to%20avoid%20dependence%20on%20the%20conventional%20energy%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20homesteaders%20choose%20an%20even%20more%20extreme%20detachment%20from%20modern%20society.%20While%20Homesteaders%20of%20America%20found%20that%20most%20survey%20respondents%20were%20employed%20full%20or%20part-time%2C%20drawing%20a%20salary%2C%20some%20off-the-grid%20communities%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foff-grid-homesteading-community-riverbed-ranch-utah-doomsday-prepper-survivalist-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERiverbed%20Ranch%20in%20the%20high%20desert%20of%20western%20Utah%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20employ%20a%20barter%20system%20where%20residents%20can%20trade%20for%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20where%20homesteaders%20lie%20on%20the%20spectrum%20from%20casual%20farmers%20to%20off-the-grid%20preppers%2C%20the%20movement%20is%2C%20at%20its%20core%2C%20a%20rejection%20of%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20lifelong%20dream%20for%20Chuck%20Anderson%2C%2061%2C%20to%20return%20to%20the%20lifestyle%20he%20experienced%20growing%20up%20on%20a%20dairy%20farm%20in%20Wisconsin.%20His%20wife%20Brooke%2C%2052%2C%20was%20quick%20to%20get%20on%20board%20with%20leaving%20their%20home%20in%20Raleigh%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20behind%20because%20the%20move%20%26quot%3Bwas%20something%20that%20brought%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20pleasure%20and%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Andersons%20purchased%20285%