's%20richest%20person%20has%20opened%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20oil%20refineries%20in%20Nigeria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAliko%20Dangote%2C%20the%20billionaire%20founder%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20multinational%20conglomerate%20the%20Dangote%20Group%2C%20opened%20the%20Dangote%20Petroleum%20Refinery%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20help%20make%20Nigeria%20self-sufficient%20in%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fafrica%2Fnigeria-commission-dangote-refinery-crude-supply-concern-2023-05-22%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%2419%20billion%20refinery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20coastal%20city%20of%20Lekki%2C%20near%20Lagos%2C%20has%20suffered%20years%20of%20delays%20and%20setbacks%2C%20but%20it%20finally%20began%20production%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Dangote%20Petroleum%20Refinery%20near%20Lagos.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aab9f3dcdb354a98590f95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dangote%20Petroleum%20Refinery%20near%20Lagos.%3Cp%3EPius%20Utomi%20Ekpei%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAppearing%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_5hYsdVbW2E%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20David%20Rubenstein%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%2C%20Dangote%20said%20oil%20made%20up%20around%2090%25%20of%20Nigeria's%20foreign%20exchange%20and%2060%25%20of%20government%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20oil-rich%20country%20must%20import%20most%20of%20its%20fuel%20due%20to%20its%20lack%20of%20refining%20facilities.%20This%20is%20something%20that%20the%20new%20Dangote%20refinery%20aims%20to%20change%20by%20eventually%20producing%20up%20to%20650%2C000%20barrels%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Rafiq%20Raji%2C%20a%20senior%20associate%20with%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20S