acter%E2%80%99s%20response%20became%20the%20seed%20of%20his%20first%20play%2C%20written%20at%20the%20age%20of%2022%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20scene%20that%20formed%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes%3A%20the%20confrontation%20between%20Yayati%20and%20Chitralekha.%20%E2%80%A6%20As%20I%20thought%20about%20it%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20play%20began%20to%20take%20shape%20around%20this%20climax.%20I%20did%20not%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20was%20writing%20a%20play%E2%80%A6%20It%20was%20as%20if%20a%20spirit%20had%20entered%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Karnad%20was%20a%20young%20man%20facing%20his%20own%20burdensome%20questions%3A%20Would%20he%20return%20to%20India%20when%20he%20was%20done%20at%20Oxford%3F%20What%20were%20his%20responsibilities%2C%20as%20a%20young%20man%2C%20to%20his%20own%20father%2C%20his%20family%2C%20or%20his%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Karnad%20wrote%20the%20play%2C%20he%20could%20relate%20to%20the%20son%2C%20Puru%2C%20and%20the%20weight%20of%20obligation%20he%20feels%20in%20the%20story.%20When%20he%20read%20the%20play%20again%2C%20much%20later%20in%20his%20own%20life%2C%20he%20found%20himself%20identifying%20with%20the%20desperation%20of%20the%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatch%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzvrEPHuVTZo%3Fsi%3DAta_8Q2EA3mEDi7o%5C%22%3EThe%20Structure%20of%20the%20Play%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20lecture%20by%20Karnad%20on%C2%A0%3Cem%3EYayati%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0at%20the%20Sahitya%20Rangabhoomi%20Pratishthan%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20story%20from%20the%20Mahabharata%20also%20made%20an%20impression%20on%20Karnad%20at%20that%20early%20point.%20This%20one%2C%20though%2C%20would%20take%2037%20years%20to%20become%20a%20play%3A%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAgni%20Mattu%20Mal%C3%A9%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Fire%20and%20the%20Rain%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%