nstead%20of%20the%20entire%20Mahabharata%2C%20they%20could%20plan%20an%20episode%20on%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20epic.%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrea%20Miller%2C%20who%20produced%20the%20series%2C%20told%20us%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20decided%20the%20series%20should%20not%20be%20solely%20based%20on%20the%20Western%20canon.%20I%E2%80%99d%20been%20very%20influenced%2C%20years%20before%2C%20by%20seeing%20Peter%20Brook%E2%80%99s%20stage%20production%20of%20The%20Mahabharata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20just%20been%20filming%20with%20Brook%20on%20another%20production%20which%20brought%20it%20all%20back%20to%20mind%E2%80%A6%20Girish%20had%20fairly%20recently%20arrived%20in%20London%20and%20had%20been%20in%20the%20newspapers%20so%20we%20contacted%20him.%20I%20recognised%20his%20work%20as%20a%20movie%20star%20of%20course.%20I%20was%20thrilled%20when%20he%20said%20yes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20episode%2C%20directed%20by%20James%20Erskine%2C%20included%20interviews%20with%20Ramachandra%20Gandhi%2C%20Mark%20Tully%20and%20(against%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20counsel%2C%20he%20later%20said)%20Murali%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20then%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20NDA-1%20government.%20Watch%20a%20selection%20of%20clips%20from%20the%20episode%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC196PinyF6r%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2AaL21SkMx%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20newsletter%20only%20scratches%20the%20surface%20of%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20life-long%20engagement%20with%20the%20epic%20%E2%80%93%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20distil%20the%20substance%20of%20his%20views%20and%20insights.%20Those%20emerge%20in%20his%20plays%20and%20in%20the%20BBC%20Gita%20documentary.%20They%20are%20there%20in%20an%20intimate%20form%2C%20too%2C%C2%A0in%20his%20studious%20notes%20on%20the%20work%20of%20professi