20the%20Republic%E2%80%99s%20honourable%20elders%3F%20Do%20the%20organisers%20and%20presiding%20officers%20of%20the%20assembly%20carry%20the%20great%20values%20of%20Indian%20civilisation%3F%20Have%20they%20offered%20their%20lives%20for%20truth%20and%20dharma%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findependence-on-january-22-the-noise-generated-around-it-bears-more-resemblance-to-force-a-divide%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Independence%E2%80%99%20on%20January%2022%3F%20The%20Noise%20Generated%20Is%20More%20Likely%20to%20Force%20a%20Divide%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%20is%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%2C%20a%20man%20known%20for%20criminal%20violence%20and%20obscene%20language%2C%20whose%20voluminous%20crime%20dossier%20has%20been%20buried%20in%20the%20state%20police%20files.%20The%20other%20person%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%2C%20so%20obsessed%20with%20reflections%20of%20himself%20everywhere%20that%20even%20Narcissus%20would%20be%20embarrassed.%20Have%20these%20elders%20lived%20a%20life%20of%20dharma%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayodhya%20assembly%20is%20founded%20on%20untruth%20and%20adharma.%20What%20its%20courtiers%20term%20as%20the%20triumph%20of%20truth%20has%20emerged%20from%20deceit%20and%20brute%20force.%20Citing%20the%20court%20ruling%2C%20they%20overlook%20that%20the%20same%20bench%20had%20termed%20the%20%E2%80%98Ayodhya%20Kand%E2%80%99%20of%20December%206%20as%20an%20offence.%20The%20above%20interpretation%20of%20Ayodhya%20becomes%20imperative%20because%20Indian%20rulers%20disregard%20the%20constitution%20and%20spread%20falsehood%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20scriptures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20a%20civilisation%20forgets%20its%20values%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20where%20are%20our%20elders%3F%20Last%20week%2C%20I%20visited%20a%20distinguished%20scholar%20and%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20finest%20thinkers.%20Approaching%2090%2C%20he%20was%20recently%20admitted%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20had%20arrived%20home%20after%20a%20difficult%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20him%20to%20discuss%20the%20biography%20of%20his%20late%20friend%2C%20Ramchandra%20Gandhi%20(grandson%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi)%2C%20that%20I%20am%20currently%20working%20on.%20He%20had%20lost%20much%20of%20his%20alertness.%20He%20was%20unable%20to%20recall%20several%20of%20his%20old%20friends%2C%20forgot%20their%20names%20and%20faces.%20His%20sentences%20trailed%20off%20in%20multiple%20directions.%20And%20yet%2C%20through%20the%20nearly%20two%20hours%20I%20spent%20with%20him%2C%20he%20had%20a%20constant%20refrain%3A%20%E2%80%9CSanatan%20dharma%20is%20in%20crisis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20take%20him%20to%20multiple%20directions%20but%20the%20old%20man%20brought%20me%20to%20the%20singular%20point.%20Amid%20fading%20memory%2C%20with%20a%20melancholically%20blank%20face%20and%20red%20eyes%2C%20he%20was%20cognisant%20enough%20to%20discern%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20greatest%20threat%20to%20the%20Indian%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0civilisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20take%20a%20clear%20stand.%20Ramu%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20faltered%2C%20and%20so%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20I%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fayodhya-rss-bjp-vhp-ram-temple%5C%22%3EFour%20Decades%20of%20Milking%20a%20Deity%20in%20Ayodhya%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReturning%20home%2C%20I%20recalled%20%3Cem%3ESita%E2%80%99s%20Kitchen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20book%20Ramchandra%20had%20written%20after%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20mosque.%20When%20the%20injured%20Hindu%20pride%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmorally%20bullied%20and%20cajoled%20to%20perceive%20a%2016th%20century%20mosque%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20the%20very%20embodiment%20of%20otherness%3B%20sheer%2C%20indissoluble%2C%20otherness%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20it%20marked%20%E2%80%9CAdvaita%E2%80%99s%20Waterloo%E2%80%9D.%20The%20philosophy%20of%20Advaita%2C%20that%20there%20is%20no%20other%2C%20which%20the%20Upnishads%20describe%20as%20%3Cem%3ETat%20Twam%20Asi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20Thou%20Art%20That%2C%20stood%20defeated%20in%20the%20inglorious%20chapter%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20Kand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20knows%20the%20famous%20Gita%20sermon%20in%20the%20Mahabharata%2C%20but%20the%20great%20epic%20has%20another%20episode%20named%20Anugita.%20The%20Pandavas%20have%20won%20the%20Hastinapur%20throne%20and%20are%20now%20the%20ruling%20kings.%20One%20day%20Arjuna%20suddenly%20realises%20that%20he%20has%20forgotten%20the%20Gita%20due%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfickleness%20of%20his%20mind%E2%80%9D.%20Admitting%20to%20his%20ignorance%2C%20Arjuna%20requests%20Krishna%20to%20deliver%20him%20the%20sermon%20all%20over%20again.%20Krishna%20rebukes%20him%20and%20says%20that%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20%E2%80%9Crecollect%20all%20what%20he%20said%20on%20that%20occasion%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20impossible%20for%20him%20to%20repeat%2C%20in%20detail%2C%20all%20that%20he%20said%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20is%2C%20perhaps%2C%20possible%20for%20a%20disciple%20to%20forget%20their%20guru%E2%80%99s%20teachings.%20But%20the%20guru%3F%20The%20great%20lord%3F%20The%20episode%20underlines%20a%20crisis%20that%20arrives%20before%20a%20civilisation%20when%20it%20forgets%20its%20values.%20The%20forgetfulness%20is%20deliberate%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Indian%20society%20and%20media.%20They%20have%20erased%20their%20recent%20past%20and%20are%20out%20to%20write%20a%20new%20history%20of%20December%206.%20Wallowing%20in%20the%20ocean%20of%20a%20sinister%20oblivion%20and%20having%20renounced%20its%20dharma%2C%20the%20Indian%20civilisation%20is%20being%20disrobed%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Ram.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20foreseen%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C