m%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsteel-authority-suspends-two-directors-at-direction-of-anti-graft-ombudsman-124012100182_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsteel-authority-suspends-two-directors-at-direction-of-anti-graft-ombudsman-124012100182_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himanta%20Sarma's%20Appeal%20To%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%20Ahead%20Of%20Ram%20Temple%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20grand%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20marks%20not%20just%20the%20triumph%20of%20Hindus%20but%20a%20triumph%20of%20the%20Indian%20civilisation%2C%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20said%2C%20appealing%20to%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20communities%20to%20organise%20special%20prayers%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20to%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20to%20organise%20special%20prayers%20tomorrow%20so%20that%20all%20of%20us%2C%20from%20all%20castes%20and%20communities%2C%20can%20stay%20together%20in%20peace.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20triumph%20of%20Hindus%2C%20but%20a%20triumph%20of%20Indian%20civilisation.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20triumph%20of%20a%20religion.%20An%20aggressor%20broke%20an%20Indian%20place%20of%20worship.%20Babar%20was%20an%20aggressor.%20He%20did%20not%20attack%20just%20Hindus.%20There%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20British%20colonialists%20and%20Babar.%20Babar%20was%20a%20foreign%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%20in%20Assamese%20during%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grand%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20coming%20up%20at%20the%20site%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20stood%20before%20its%20demolition%20in%201992.%20The%2016th%20century%20mosque%20had%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20an%20age-old%20dispute%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20The%20Hindus%20believe%20that%20the%20site%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20that%20Muslim%20invaders%20razed%20a%20temple%20there%20and%20built%20the%20mosque.%20Inscriptions%20inside%20the%20now%20demolished%20mosque%20suggested%20it%20was%20built%20in%201528-29%20by%20Mir%20Baqi%2C%20a%20commander%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Babur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20decades-long%20legal%20battles%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202019%20handed%20over%20the%20disputed%20site%20to%20a%20trust%20to%20build%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%20The%20court%20asked%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20to%20give%20land%20to%20the%20Sunni%20Central%20Waqf%20Board%20for%20building%20a%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ayodhya%20gets%20ready%20for%20the%20grand%20pran%20pratistha%20ceremony%2C%20which%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Assam%20has%20declared%20holiday%20for%20schools%2C%20colleges%20and%20universities%20tomorrow.%20These%20include%20private%20institutions%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20the%20centre's%20half-day%20break%20to%20government%20employees%2C%20Assam%20has%20said%20state%20government%20offices%20will%20be%20shut%20till%202.30%20pm.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20also%20declared%20tomorrow%20a%20dry%20day.%20Fish%20and%20meat%20shops%2C%20it%20has%20said%2C%20will%20remain%20closed%20till%204%20pm.%20Also%2C%20restaurants%20will%20be%20barred%20from%20serving%20non-vegetarian%20items%20till%202%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20appeal%20to%20business%20establishments%20to%20shut%20shops%20during%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Ram%20Temple%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20said%20special%20security%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20in%20sensitive%20areas%20to%20prevent%20any%20communal%20flare-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705823700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fu743q1go_himanta-biswa-sarma_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nd