ontent%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12170059%2FEffect-27.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20has%20given%20a%20fillip%20to%20Hindutva%20leaders%20to%20reassert%20their%20dream%20of%20creating%20an%20%E2%80%9CAkhand%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20they%20believe%20is%20an%20integrated%20land%20patch%20comprising%20present-day%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Tibet%20and%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20several%20Hindutva%20organisations%20have%20begun%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20supposed%20%E2%80%9CAkhand%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20chief%20minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Mohan%20Yadav%20on%20Saturday%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20God%20wishes%2C%20%E2%80%98Akhand%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20formed%20again%2C%20if%20not%20today%2C%20then%20tomorrow%3B%20not%20only%20up%20to%20Sindh%20or%20Punjab%20but%20even%20till%20Afghanistan%E2%80%A6%20we%20should%20be%20able%20to%20visit%20Nankana%20Sahib%20(a%20prominent%20Sikh%20pilgrim%20site%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Punjab%20province).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20was%20speaking%20at%20a%20religious%20function%20at%20Bairagarh%20near%20Bhopal.%20He%20said%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20a%20%E2%80%9CRam%20Rajya%20(ideal%20state)%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20possible%20recovery%20from%20the%20losses%20made%20by%20India%20after%20the%20partition%20in%201947%20when%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20lost%20Sindh%2C%20Punjab%20was%20divided%2C%20and%20Pakistan%20was%20formed%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fakhand-bharat-will-happen-one-day-says-mp-cm%2Farticle67760103.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20added%20that%20King%20Vikramaditya%20built%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20temple%20but%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthorn%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20enemies%E2%80%9D%20who%20destroyed%20it.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20being%20reconstructed%20after%20a%20political%20struggle%20of%2030-32%20years.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20for%20the%20last%20500%20years%2C%20several%20generations%20passed%20in%20it%20(the%20struggle)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20president%20V.D.%20Sharma%20made%20a%20similar%20speech%20where%20he%20said%20if%20given%20a%20chance%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20will%20also%20change%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cgeography%E2%80%9D.%20Sharma%20urged%20people%20to%20give%20the%20BJP%20another%20chance%20at%20the%20Centre%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20saffron%20flag%20is%20hoisted%20in%20Lahore%20and%20Karachi.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20one%20who%20is%20building%20a%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20one%20who%20is%20building%20the%20corridor%20of%20Baba%20Vishwanath%2C%20has%20removed%20Article%20370.%20Give%20us%20another%20chance%2C%20we%20will%20show%20you%20by%20changing%20the%20geography%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20role%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20these%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20declared%20a%20holiday%20for%20all%20schools%20and%20colleges%20and%20a%20half-day%20leave%20for%20government%20employees%20on%20January%2022%20when%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20will%20be%20inaugurated.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20also%20ordered%20a%20complete%20shutdown%20of%20meat%20shops%20and%20slaughterhouses%20on%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705823120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12170059%2FEffect-27.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fakhand-bharat-will-be-formed-again-says-mps-bjp-cm-mohan-yadav%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20said%20the%20